.TH ai-profiles-location "1" "February 2026" "SMI Toolset" "AI Profiles Command"
.SH NAME
ai-profiles-location \- print the AI profiles directory path
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B ai-profiles-location
.SH DESCRIPTION
The
.B ai-profiles-location
command prints the absolute path to the AI profiles directory, which
resides under the SMI library location returned by
.BR smi-lib-location (1).
.PP
Typically this resolves to:
.I /opt/setmy.info/lib/profiles/ai
on standard installations.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR smi-lib-location (1),
.BR ai (1)
